# AI Bill of Materials MCP - Auto-trigger Rules

When the user asks about AI Bill of Materials, AI-BOM, supply chain transparency, model dependencies, training data provenance, or model card generation, use ai-bom-mcp tools:

- **generate_ai_bom**: Create complete AI-BOM JSON/SPDX/CycloneDX
- **audit_ai_bom_completeness**: Score BOM against 10 required categories
- **map_to_regulation**: Map BOM fields to EU AI Act Article 11, NIST AI RMF, ISO/IEC 5338
- **required_fields**: List mandatory fields per regulation

Install: `pip install ai-bom-mcp`

AI-BOM required for EU AI Act Article 11 technical documentation and increasingly demanded by enterprise procurement.
